{"tid":1606233,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔好比我見到一味死打陣地戰！要Be Water！","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:22:04.000Z","uid":262035,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c30c82948b910ab0aa8c4c2cd611dc9d8ef07940","tid":1606233,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"講左好耐打Total War 呢隻Game<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好死打陣地戰！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打陣地戰對自己勢力黎講係完全無優勢可言！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一、兵力聚埋一堆係好易比人包圍</span></span><br />\n兵力聚埋一齊就好似一個圓餅咁，入面有既人好多，但敵人包圍只需要好少人。無理由明知對手比己方弱既地方係人少，我地仲咁固執打陣地戰比對手包。如果敵人包到唔留空位，就只會變左甕中捉鱉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、陣地戰有利敵人部署戰術</span></span><br />\n試問打仗既時候，有咩係好打過企定定唔郁既對手？你唔郁，敵人就可以慢慢安排戰略，調度好人手先再出擊。最終形勢只會變左敵暗我明，自己啲兵只會墮入哂敵人既圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、陣地戰係好無效益既戰術</span></span><br />\n大家諗下打陣地戰既時候有幾多兵係idle左？明明呢啲兵可以分散敵人注意力同兵力，但偏偏放埋一邊無所事事咁。點解唔釋放呢啲儲備兵既潛能，幫手拉打對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">四、陣地戰太多人聚埋一齊不利撤退</span></span><br />\n玩過total war 都知，啲兵聚埋一齊只會阻住隊友走。明明個部隊移動速度高，但比自己人塞住，搞到比對手滅左又為乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以千祈唔好再打陣地戰<br />\n要分小隊咁打游擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣先可以分散敵人兵源<br />\n令對手疲於奔命<br />\n而且令到戰略效益最大化！"},{"pid":"d929d80b094530360bf377871a3b32b1d4f2e136","tid":1606233,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"開錯台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4cbe55802b1ef96f76d83889029bb985fdeefb","tid":1606233,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713ad8ff111d33d5f0dd1a8e8c2169afc4612f93","tid":1606233,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"大家係咪都唔玩total war 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170744ab5150f97f1b6cfa5958cd3af90dc1b677","tid":1606233,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"p 牌推唔到<br />\n有冇人幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ed1742c03a8077996634e894de3897b31717ce","tid":1606233,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dd311668d313a3b5d840b79cd6ffe77524d3e7","tid":1606233,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"846b1f25f1305de38f89abc01d7ed4e6bd97b083","tid":1606233,"uid":254044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2a9c9e04d4f58dd38b1895918e16f0a2fb36553","tid":1606233,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"唔好逗留<br />\n快速移動"}]}